{"word":"H8113 - שִׁמְרִי - Shimrîy - shim-ree' - Shimri","slug":"H8113","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שִׁמְרִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Shimrîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shim-ree'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shimri"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>שׁמרי</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>shimrı̂y</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>shim-ree'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Shimri = \"vigilant\" <ol><li>a Simeonite, son of Shemaiah and father of Jedaiah</li><li>father of Jediael, one of David's mighty warriors</li><li>a Merarite Levite, son of Hosah</li><li>a Kohathite Levite of the sons of Elizaphan</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H8105\">H8105</a> in its original sense <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3461\">H3461</a>, <a href=\"#/H4929\">H4929</a>, <a href=\"#/H4931\">H4931</a>, <a href=\"#/H7763\">H7763</a>, <a href=\"#/H8104\">H8104</a>, <a href=\"#/H8106\">H8106</a>, <a href=\"#/H8107\">H8107</a>, <a href=\"#/H8108\">H8108</a>, <a href=\"#/H8109\">H8109</a>, <a href=\"#/H8110\">H8110</a>, <a href=\"#/H8111\">H8111</a>, <a href=\"#/H8112\">H8112</a>, <a href=\"#/H8114\">H8114</a>, <a href=\"#/H8116\">H8116</a>, <a href=\"#/H8117\">H8117</a>, <a href=\"#/H8118\">H8118</a>, <a href=\"#/H8119\">H8119</a>, <a href=\"#/H821\">H821</a>"}]}